const watches = [{
        id: 1,
        brand: "Rolex",
        model: "Submariner Date",
        description: "The Rolex Submariner Date is an iconic diving watch featuring a 41mm Oystersteel case, black Cerachrom bezel, and automatic movement. Water-resistant to 300 meters with a power reserve of 70 hours. This legendary timepiece combines robust construction with timeless elegance.",
        price: 98500,
        condition: "New",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523170335258-f5ed11844a49?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
    },
    {
        id: 2,
        brand: "Patek Philippe",
        model: "Nautilus 5711",
        description: "The legendary Patek Philippe Nautilus 5711 features a 40mm stainless steel case, iconic porthole design, and automatic caliber 26-330 S C movement. This pre-owned piece is in excellent condition and represents one of the most sought-after luxury sports watches in the world.",
        price: 1250000,
        condition: "Pre-owned",
        image: "https://media.gettyimages.com/id/531725359/photo/rolex-wrist-watch.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=OqHPFuSIlt6qKDKOHfTf8jtEWcknOHgaR5A6NkJg1kc="
    },
    {
        id: 3,
        brand: "Audemars Piguet",
        model: "Royal Oak",
        description: "The Audemars Piguet Royal Oak showcases the legendary octagonal bezel and integrated bracelet design. This 41mm model in stainless steel features the 'Grande Tapisserie' dial pattern and houses the automatic Calibre 4302 movement with 70-hour power reserve.",
        price: 420000,
        condition: "New",
        image: "https://media.gettyimages.com/id/458132157/photo/gold-rolex-gmt-master-2-wristwatch.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=I-UcACBAoQFZUoVoQAk0aFuA-8WXGuBhyG5AZlgmwa8="
    },
    {
        id: 4,
        brand: "Omega",
        model: "Speedmaster Professional",
        description: "The Omega Speedmaster Professional 'Moonwatch' is the legendary chronograph that went to the moon. Features a 42mm stainless steel case, hesalite crystal, manual-wind caliber 1861 movement, and the iconic tachymeter bezel. A true piece of horological history.",
        price: 58000,
        condition: "New",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587836374828-4dbafa94cf0e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
    },
    {
        id: 5,
        brand: "Rolex",
        model: "Cosmograph Daytona",
        description: "The Rolex Cosmograph Daytona is the ultimate racing chronograph. This pre-owned piece features a 40mm Oystersteel case, black Cerachrom bezel, and automatic chronograph movement. Water-resistant to 100 meters with exceptional precision and reliability.",
        price: 350000,
        condition: "Pre-owned",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1614164185128-e4ec99c436d7?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        brand: "Cartier",
        model: "Santos de Cartier",
        description: "The Cartier Santos de Cartier is a timeless classic with a square case design and exposed screws. This large model features a stainless steel case and bracelet, automatic movement, and the signature blue sword-shaped hands. Elegant and versatile.",
        price: 75000,
        condition: "New",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594534475808-b18fc33b045e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        brand: "Patek Philippe",
        model: "Calatrava 5196",
        description: "The Patek Philippe Calatrava 5196 epitomizes dress watch elegance. Features a 37mm white gold case, silvery opaline dial, and manual-wind caliber 215 PS movement. This understated masterpiece represents refined luxury at its finest.",
        price: 285000,
        condition: "New",
        image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523170335258-f5ed11844a49?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80"
    }
];

export default watches;
